Interpreter notes

Delimeters supported by lexical analyzer:

  • == += -= *= /= = != <= >= <<= >>=
  • := === !== << >>
  • , ; : ( ) { } [ ] < > + - * / ! =
  • ++ --
  • && ||
  • ^ # ~
  • . ->

Precedence of operations:

  1. LOWEST: := = += -= *= /= %= <<= >>=
  2. ||
  3. &&
  4. === == != !==
  5. < > <= >=
  6. << >>
  7. + -
  8. * /
  9. HIGHEST:
    • (expr) - parentheses
    • built-in function call
    • var var^
    • binary []
    • prefix unary
    • postfix unary
